title: Catherine Coulter-Backfire
description: the mysterious note delivered to FBI agent Dillon Savich has him and his partner, Lacey Sherlock, on edge, just as they're starting an investigation into the shooting of their longtime friend Ramsey Hunt. The San Francisco judge was shot in the back during a high-profile murder trial?and now Sherlock's and Savich's search for the truth will take a shocking turn that no one could have seen coming?
